    <div class="assump-card">
      <div class="ac-title">Terminal Growth</div>
      <div class="ac-value">{(growthRateTerminal * 100).toFixed(1)}%</div>
      <div class="ac-desc">After year 5, we assume FCF grows at 3% perpetually. This is slightly above standard GDP growth, reflecting the long-term structural tailwinds for memory chips globally.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="assump-card">
      <div class="ac-title">Discount Rate</div>
      <div class="ac-value">{(discountRate * 100).toFixed(0)}%</div>
      <div class="ac-desc">Memory is a notoriously cyclical, capital-intensive industry. We require an 11% return to compensate for this elevated beta and cyclical risk, higher than a typical large-cap.</div>
